title: Radio Show Hour 1 - 03/29/2021
creator: Liberty Roundtable Podcast
subject: Podcast
description: * Guest: Lowell Nelson - CampaignForLiberty.org - RonPaulInstitute.org.* Call to Action: Stop the \"Legalized Election Theft\" Bills HR 1 / S 1!* Want a Job? Get a Shot! - Ron Paul - \"Politicians and bureaucrats have used overblown fear of coronavirus to justify the largest infringement of individual liberty in modern times. Covid tyranny has been aided by many Americans who are not just willing to sacrifice their liberty for phony security, but who help government take away liberty from their fellow citizens.\"* States Just Need to Say No! - Mike Maharrey.* Ron Paul on the passage of legislation banning mandatory COVID vaccines in Wisconsin - \"If governments can force individuals to receive vaccines and other medical treatments against their will, there is no area of life safe from government mandates. All who value liberty should celebrate the Wisconsin Assembly's passage of legislation forbidding government officials from mandating any individual receive the COVID vaccine.\"* Show Me Your Papers Please: NY Governor Andrew Cuomo announced that \"New York has rolled out the nation's first COVID vaccine passport program with the introduction of the \"Excelsior Pass.\"* Florida: Magic Kingdom Says COVID-19 is Reason to Install Facial Recognition.* Update: Michigan Pizzeria Owner Released from Jail - The passport will be rolled out as a voluntary system, businesses will be coerced into complying.
